            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1715615776491-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1715615776491-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Peruvian-style chicken</strong> over the <strong>aji amarillo-style sauce </strong>with the <strong>chickpea salad </strong>and <strong>garlic butter rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
